## Summary

✗ **Bug found**: Created bug report file `bug_report_lxml_doctestcompare_2025-08-18_05-33_5xgt.md`

The property-based testing discovered a genuine logic bug in `lxml.doctestcompare.LXMLOutputChecker.text_compare` where whitespace normalization is inconsistent when certain whitespace characters (like `\r`) appear before the `...` wildcard. The bug causes valid pattern matches to fail.
